g.%20It%20was%20reverse-swinging%20in%20the%2015th.%20Umpires%20need%20to%20keep%20their%20eyes%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20Inzamam%20told%20the%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInzamam%20further%20stated%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Pakistan%20bowlers%20did%20this%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20hue%20and%20cry.%20We%20know%20how%20to%20reverse%20it%20really%20well.%20If%20Arshdeep%20can%20reverse%20it%20in%20the%2015th%2C%20there's%20been%20some%20serious%20work%20done%20on%20the%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Bumrah%20does%20it%20(you%20can%20understand)%2C%20his%20action%20is%20like%20that.%20When%20others%20with%20a%20specific%20action%20or%20speed%20do%20it%2C%20it%20means%20the%20ball%20has%20been%20prepared%20in%20a%20special%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Inzamam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20was%20asked%20about%20Inzamam's%20comment%20in%20the%20pre-match%20media%20interaction%20here%20and%20he%20dismissed%20it%2C%20advising%20the%20former%20batter%20to%20have%20an%20open%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAbhi%20kya%20jawab%20du%20iska%20mein%20bhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(what%20answer%20should%20I%20give%2C%20brother).%20Wickets%20are%20so%20dry%20(here)%20as%20you%20are%20playing%20in%20a%20sunny%20weather.%20All%20teams%20are%20getting%20reverse%20(swing).%20Sometimes%20%3Cem%3Edimaag%20ko%20kholna%20zaroori%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Need%20to%20open%20your%20mind).%20You%20need%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20conditions%20are.%20This%20is%20not%20Australia%20or%20England.%20That's%20what%20I%20will%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20to%20respond%20to%20Inzamam's%20observation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22in%5C%22%3EInzamam%20ul%20haq%20%26quot%3BDimag%20ko%20kholo%20Bhikhari%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnROHIT%20SHARMA%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BIND%20vs%20ENG%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FINDvENG%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3