erving%20any%20jail%20time%20for%20now%20and%20will%20receive%20mental%20health%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharmesh%20Patel%2C%20a%20radiologist%20in%20California%2C%20drove%20his%20car%2C%20carrying%20his%20wife%20Neha%20and%20two%20children%20aged%207%20and%204%2C%20off%20a%20cliff%20last%20year%20after%20suffering%20from%20a%20psychotic%20breakdown%2C%20psychologists%20told%20the%20court.%20Mr%20Patel%20believed%20his%20children%20were%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20sex%20trafficked%20which%20led%20him%20to%20crash%20the%20car%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20driving%20off%20the%20cliff%2C%20the%20Tesla%20fell%20over%20250%20feet.%20However%2C%20the%20family%20miraculously%20survived%20the%20crash%20and%20was%20rescued%20from%20the%20mangled%20car.%20After%20being%20rescued%2C%20his%20wife%20admitted%20that%20he%20drove%20the%20car%20off%20the%20cliff%20intentionally%20but%20testified%20later%20that%20she%20did%20not%20want%20her%20husband%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20doctors%2C%20Mr%20Patel%20was%20suffering%20from%20schizoaffective%20disorder%20and%20major%20depressive%20disorder%20weeks%20before%20the%20crash.%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20been%20hearing%20footsteps%20and%20thought%20he%20was%20being%20followed%20in%20the%20weeks%20before%20the%20crash.%20It%20was%20paranoid%20and%20kind%20of%20delusional%20thinking%20that%20he%20acted%20on%20at%20the%20time%20to%20protect%20his%20family%20from%20a%20worse%20fate%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20psychologist%20told%20the%20court%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20concerned%20that%20his%20children%20were%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20kidnapped%2C%20possibly%20for%20sexual%20molestation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20a%20US%20court%20decided%20that%20Mr%20Patel%20was%20eligible%20for%20a%20'mental%20health%20diversion'%2C%20that%20allows%20an%20accused%20with%20mental%20illness%20who%20has%20committed%20a%20crime%20to%20get%20mental%20health%20treatment%20instead%20of%20serving%20jail%20time.%20The%20law%20states%20that%20such%20a%20provision%20can%20only%20be%20considered%20if%20the%20illness%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperior%20Court%20Judge%20Susan%20M.%20Jakubowski%20deemed%20Mr%20Patel%20eligible%20for%20the%20program%20based%20on%20the%20doctors'%20diagnosis%20and%20ordered%20he%20be%20released%20to%20his%20parents%20in%20California.%20He%20will%20be%20monitored%20with%20GPS%20and%20report%20to%20the%20court%20once%20a%20week.%20He%20is%20also%20not%20allowed%20to%20travel%20outside%20his%20country%20and%20must%20surrender%20his%20driving%20license%20and%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20will%20be%20held%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719453180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcdjgbo3s_indian-doctor-crime-us_625x300_28_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fno-jail-for-indian-origin-doctor-who-drove-wife-2-children-off-cliff-in-us-5978653%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-American%20doctor%20who%20drove%20his%20Tesla%20off%20a%20cliff%20in%20the%20US%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20inside%20-%20in%20an%20alleged%20attempt%20to%20murder%20them%20-%20will%20not%20be%20serving%20any%20jail%20time%20for%20now%20and%20will%20receive%20mental%20health%20treatment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fno-jail-for-indian-origin-doctor-who-drove-wife-2-children-off-cliff-in-us-5978653%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fno-jail-for-indian-origin-doctor-who-drove-wife-2-children-off-cliff-in-us-5978653%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fno-jail-for-indian-origin-doctor-who-drove-wife-2-children-off-cliff-in-us-5978653%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%2