0amplify%20the%20signal%20of%20FPV%20drones%20loaded%20with%20explosives%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20Kharkiv%20region%2C%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EPablo%20Miranzo%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShotguns%20found%20a%20new%20niche%20role%20in%20modern%20warfare%20as%20low-tech%2C%20effective%20anti-drone%20weapons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECommercial%20drones%20are%20becoming%20standard%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECountries%20like%20France%2C%20Belgium%2C%20and%20the%20US%20are%20also%20looking%20to%20adopt%20shotguns%20to%20counter%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shotgun's%20role%20in%20warfare%20has%20had%20an%20interesting%20development.%20During%20the%20Revolutionary%20War%2C%20the%20famed%20buck-and-ball%20loadings%20proved%20to%20be%20remarkably%20efficient%20at%20ensuring%20the%20Red%20Coats%20stayed%20red.%20In%20the%20Civil%20War%2C%20the%20Confederacy%20often%20lacked%20rifles%2C%20and%20mounted%20troops%20with%20muzzle-loaded%20shotguns%20wreaked%20havoc%20on%20horseback.%20World%20War%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fthe-trench-guns-of-world-war-i%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emade%20them%20trench%20guns%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20World%20War%20II%20jungle%20guns.%20The%20GWOT%20had%20them%20knocking%20down%20doors%2C%20and%20in%202024%2C%20shotguns%20found%20a%20new%20niche%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20cheap%2C%20mass-produced%2C%20civilian%2C%20and%20even%20toy-grade%20drones%20has%20changed%20the%20battlefield.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20drones%20are%20the%20new%20Improvised%20Explosive%20Devices.%20They%20are%20a%20new%2C%20extremely%20dangerous%20threat%20that%20doesn't%20comply%20with%20the%20tactics%20we'd%20been%20taught%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20The%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20cemented%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A