3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20common%20uses%20of%20shotguns%20is%20hitting%20flying%20targets%2C%20this%20could%20include%20birds%20and%20clay%20pigeons%20%E2%80%94%20but%20drones%20are%20also%20flying%20targets%2C%20so%20shotguns%20are%20their%20natural%20predators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefit%20of%20shotguns%20is%20that%20they%20are%20low-tech%20and%20easily%20available.%20Further%2C%20shotguns%20are%20fairly%20lightweight%20weapons%20and%20could%20be%20carried%20by%20a%20designated%20troop%20alongside%20a%20service%20rifle.%20Sure%2C%20it%20sucks%20to%20carry%20two%20guns%2C%20but%20it%20also%20sucks%20to%20get%20a%20grenade%20dropped%20on%20you%20from%20a%20tiny%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20shot%20option%20to%20take%20out%20drones%20would%20be%20birdshot%2C%20specifically%2C%20heavy%20birdshot%20made%20for%20shooting%20geese%20and%20similar%20large%20fowls.%20The%20pellets%20wouldn't%20even%20have%20to%20completely%20destroy%20the%20drone%3B%20instead%2C%20just%20a%20few%20pellets%20hitting%20the%20propellers%20or%20body%20could%20destabilize%20it%20enough%20to%20render%20it%20ineffective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20shotgun%20type%2C%20semi-auto%20would%20work%20best%20as%20they%20allow%20for%20quick%20follow-up%20shots%20in%20case%20of%20a%20miss.%20(Pump-action%20shotguns%20could%20also%20work%3A%20although%20they%20require%20the%20manual%20movement%20of%20a%20pump%20to%20chamber%20the%20next%20cartridge%2C%20they%20would%20still%20offer%20a%20fairly%20fast%20second%20shot.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f026d1b-660f-44f1-a649-6b55bc5240c2%5C%22%3EA%20proven%20concept%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22792%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soldiers%20fire%20at%20an%20unmanned%20aerial%20vehicle%20from%20a%20FREMM-class%20frigate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c8e97d1c84a0eaca822e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22445%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESoldiers%20fire%20at%20an%20unmanned%20aerial%20vehicle%20from%20a%20FREMM-class%20frigate.%3Cp%3EFrench%20Ministry%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20French%20Armed%20Forces%20chose%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fthis-is-why-france-chose-the-benelli-supernova-as-its-new-shotgun%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBenelli%20Supernova%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2012-gauge%20as%20their%20shotgun%20and%20adopted%20tactical%20models%20with%2018-%20and%2014-inch%20long%20barrels.%20However%2C%20they%20also%20adopted%20a%2028-inch%20barreled%20model%20to%20serve%20as%20an%20anti-drone%20weapon%2C%20as%20the%20longer%20barrel%20offers%20a%20longer%20sight%20radius%20and%20better%20swing%20for%20dealing%20with%20flying%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supernova%20also%20offers%20a%203.5-inch%20chamber%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20some%20hefty%20rounds%20with%20lots%20of%20shot%20dispersed.%20(The%203.5-inch%20rounds%20are%20popular%20with%20bird%20hunters%20because%20of%20all%20the%20shot%20they%20can%20hold.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supernova%20is%20an%20interesting%20choice%20but%20fairly%20standard%20compared%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20armed%20forces%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.armyrecognition.com%2Fnews%2Farmy-news%2F2024%2Fukraine-adopts-turkish-bts-12-shotgun-for-anti-drone-warfare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epurchased%20several%20thousand%20Turkish%20Hatsan%20shotguns%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20bullpup%20configuration.%20This%20means%20the%20magazine%20and%20action%20are%20behind%20the%20trigger%2C%20making%20the%20weapon%20shorter%2C%20which%20is%20nice%20for%20armored%20troops.%20However%2C%20Turkish%20shotguns%20have%20a%20poor%20reputation%20for%20reliability%2C%20and%20I%20imagine%20the%20battlefield%20will%20beat%20them%20to%20hell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Belgians%20adopted%20the%20Benelli%20M4%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20best%20fighting%20shotguns%2C%20for%20anti-drone%20work.%20The%20United%20States%20is%20experimenting%20with%20both%20shotguns%20and%20electronic%20countermeasures%20against%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229aaf349f-deb6-4407-8fbe-7e53ced84557%5C%22%3EThe%20downside%20of%20shotguns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20servicemen%20scan%20the%20sky%20for%20Russian%20drones%20and%20aircraft%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c911f40cf2af6e4f61211%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20servicemen%20scan%20the%20sky%20for%20Russian%20drones%20and%20aircraft%20at%20a%20position%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20region%20of%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EGenya%20Savilov%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShotguns%20have%20a%20very%20limited%20range%2C%20and%20even%20with%20the%20best%20birdshot%2C%20we%20are%20looking%20at%2050%20yards%20at%20most.%20Yet%2C%20drones%20can%20fly%20higher%20than%20that.%20Specialized%20munitions%20could%20potentially%20resolve%20that%2C%20and%20they%20do%20exist%20in%20the%20form%20of%20various%20net%20devices.%20Still%2C%20those%20create%20a%20logistic-chain%20issue%20versus%20standard%20off-the-shelf%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20their%20limitations%2C%20shotguns%20prevent%20drones%20from%20getting%20too%20close.%20The%20closer%20a%20drone%20can%20get%20with%20a%20droppable%20munition%2C%20the%20more%20accurate%20it%20tends%20to%20be.%20Also%2C%20drone%20cameras%20don't%20always%20provide%20the%20clearest%20footage%2C%20which%20can%20force%20a%20drone%20to%20fly%20lower%20to%20spot%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShotguns%20won't%20be%20the%20ultimate%2C%20end-all%20option%20against%20commercial%20drones%2C%20but%20they%20are%20an%20infantry%20and%20armor%20or