en%20CPR%20certified%20as%20a%20teen%2C%20but%20my%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20now%2012%2C%2014%20and%2016%20%E2%80%94%20were%20learning%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20never%20imagined%20that%20my%20middle%20son%2C%20Trevor%2C%20would%20soon%20be%20using%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-uses-cpr-to-save-daughters-life-at-cheer-competition-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eskills%20to%20save%20a%20life%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20right%20in%20our%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257014f24-dc0a-449e-b68a-2000dc5eb132%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son's%20wrestling%20teammate%20collapsed%20at%20our%20house%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20boys%20love%20to%20wrestle.%20We%20have%20a%20home%20gym%20that%20we%20call%20The%20Barn%2C%20with%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreadmill-desk-walking-pad-not-worth-it-year-later-review-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etreadmill%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20weights%2C%20and%20a%20wrestling%20area%2C%20so%20it's%20normal%20for%20kids%20on%20the%20high%20school%20wrestling%20team%20to%20stop%20by.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20May%2010th%20two%20of%20my%20sons'%20fellow%20wrestlers%20came%20over%3A%20Giovanni%20Scafidi%20and%20J.J%20Machnik%2C%20a%20senior%20who%20was%20captain%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20boys%20headed%20into%20the%20basement%2C%20while%20Trevor%20was%20still%20upstairs.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20kitchen%20when%20I%20heard%20the%20treadmill%20start.%20About%20five%20minutes%20later%20I%20heard%20a%20crash%2C%20then%20Giovanni%20screaming%20J.J.'s%20name.%20The%20way%20he%20said%20it%20I%20knew%20something%20was%20very%20wrong.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJ.J%20had%20wrestled%20with%20my%20older%20son%20since%20they%20were%20little%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20he%20had%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-of-heart-problems-for-young-adults-from-a-cardiologist-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eheart%20condition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20dialed%20911%20before%20I%20even%20got%20to%20the%20basement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fcde6ce-cec4-4890-8ae7-30e646f44162%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETrevor%20started%20CPR%20while%20I%20spoke%20to%20911%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrevor%20had%20run%20down%20from%20his%20room%2C%20and%20he%20and%20Giovanni%20were%20taking%20care%20of%20J.J.%20%E2%80%94%20rolling%20him%20onto%20his%20back%20and%20getting%20some%20of%20his%20bulky%20clothes%20off%20him%20%E2%80%94%20while%20I%20spoke%20with%20the%20911%20dispatcher.%20The%20dispatcher%20kept%20asking%20if%20J.J.%20was%20breathing.%20At%20first%20he%20was%2C%20but%20the%20next%20time%20I%20asked%2C%20the%20boys%20paused%20to%20listen%20for%20breath%20and%20heard%20nothing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20when%20Trevor%20stepped%20into%20action.%20He%20was%20only%20in%20eighth%20grade%20but%20he%20gave%20J.J.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupermarket-cashier-performed-cpr-for-23-minutes-humming-bee-gees-song-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echest%20compressions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20prompted%20Giovanni%20for%20when%20to%20give%20rescue%20breaths.%20The%20boys%20kept%20up%20CPR%20until%20the%20first%20responders%20arrived%20about%20five%20minutes%20afterward.%20Later%2C%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20said%20the%20efficient%20CPR%20that%20Trevor%20delivered%20likely%20saved%20J.J.'s%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22efef5487-968b-4ffc-9645-e2529fcb345a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20police%20officer%20tried%20to%20prepare%20me%20for%20the%20worst%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20though%2C%20we%20didn't%20know%20if%20J.J.%20would%20make%20it.%20I%20had%20called%20his%20mother%2C%20Laura%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-child-called-911-wanted-hug-from-deputy-florida-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehung%20up%20with%20911%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20was%20in%20auto-pilot%2C%20and%20told%20her%20that%20J.J.%20had%20collapsed%20and%20she%20had%20to%20get%20to%20my%20house%20immediately.%20She%20was%20about%2020%20minutes%20away%20at%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrevor%2C%20Giovanni%2C%20and%20I%20went%20upstairs%20to%20give%20the%20first%20responders%20room%20to%20work%20on%20J.J.%20We%20later%20learned%20they%20intubated%20him%20right%20in%20the%20basement%20and%20continued%20CPR%20the%20whole%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%20while%20one%20of%20the%20police%20came%20up%20to%20talk%20to%20me.%20I%20think%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20prepare%20me.%20They%20were%20doing%20their%20best%2C%20but%20J.J.'s%20heart%20was%20working%20against%20them.%20Even%20with%20a%20shock%20from%20the%20AED%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20continue%20beating.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaura%20arrived%20just%20as%20J.J.%20was%20loaded%20into%20the%20ambulance.%20As%20they%20went%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20boys%20and%20I%20were%20left%20at%20home%2C%20shocked%20and%20praying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22878a3247-4ff3-4075-aecf-f393e744e996%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20visited%20J.J.%20in%20the%20hospital%20on%20his%2019th%20birthday%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20the%20day%2C%20Laura%20called%20me%20with%20updates.%20I%20was%20afraid%20to%20answer%20the%20phone%20each%20time%2C%20because%20the%20prognosis%20wasn't%20good.%20There%20was%20hope%20though%2C%20since%20J.J.%20was%20able%20to%20see%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffindadoctor.atlantichealth