e%20withdrawn%2C%26quot%3B%20Ruto%20told%20a%20press%20briefing.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20have%20spoken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20proposing%20an%20engagement%20with%20the%20young%20people%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20our%20sons%20and%20daughters%2C%20for%20us%20to%20listen%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20in%20a%20marked%20shift%20from%20his%20late-night%20address%20Tuesday%20when%20he%20likened%20some%20of%20the%20demonstrators%20to%20%26quot%3Bcriminals%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Cannot%20kill%20all%20of%20us'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20his%20speech%2C%20prominent%20protester%20Hanifa%20Adan%20dismissed%20Ruto's%20announcement%20as%20%26quot%3BPR%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20his%20comments%20the%20previous%20night%2C%20she%20said%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20made%20that%20speech%20trying%20to%20intimidate%20us%20and%20he%20saw%20it%20won't%20work%20hence%20the%20PR.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20is%20withdrawn%20but%20are%20you%20going%20to%20bring%20everyone%20that%20died%20back%20alive%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20Ruto's%20about-turn%2C%20protesters%20had%20called%20for%20fresh%20rallies%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTomorrow%2C%20we%20march%20peacefully%20again%20as%20we%20wear%20white%2C%20for%20all%20our%20fallen%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Adan%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20kill%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemonstrators%20shared%20%26quot%3BTupatane%20Thursday%26quot%3B%20(%26quot%3Bwe%20meet%20Thursday%26quot%3B%20in%20Swahili)%2C%20alongside%20the%20hashtag%20%23Rejectfinancebill2024%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECost-of-living%20crisis%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuto%20came%20to%20power%20in%202022%20promising%20to%20champion%20the%20needs%20of%20impoverished%20Kenyans%2C%20but%20tax%20increases%20under%20his%20government%20have%20only%20made%20life%20tougher%20for%20those%20already%20struggling%20with%20high%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kenyan%20leader%20had%20already%20rolled%20back%20some%20tax%20measures%20last%20week%2C%20prompting%20the%20treasury%20to%20warn%20of%20a%20gaping%20budget%20shortfall%20of%20200%20billion%20shillings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuto%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20withdrawing%20the%20bill%20would%20mean%20a%20significant%20hole%20in%20funding%20for%20development%20programmes%20to%20help%20farmers%20and%20schoolteachers%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cash-strapped%20government%20had%20said%20previously%20that%20the%20increases%20were%20needed%20to%20service%20Kenya's%20massive%20debt%20of%20some%2010%20trillion%20shillings%20(%2478%20billion)%2C%20equal%20to%20roughly%2070%20percent%20of%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeadly%20day%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Roseline%20Odede%2C%20chairwoman%20of%20the%20state-funded%20Kenya%20National%20Commission%20on%20Human%20Rights%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20recorded%2022%20deaths%26quot%3B%2C%2019%20of%20them%20in%20Nairobi%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20would%20launch%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20deaths%20(in)%20a%20single%20day%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20300%20people%20were%20injured%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimon%20Kigondu%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Kenya%20Medical%20Association%2C%20said%20he%20had%20never%20before%20seen%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20level%20of%20violence%20against%20unarmed%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20at%20Kenyatta%20National%20Hospital%20in%20Nairobi%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20medics%20were%20treating%20%26quot%3B160%20people...some%20of%20them%20with%20soft%20tissue%20injuries%2C%20some%20of%20them%20with%20bullet%20wounds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERights%20watchdogs%20have%20also%20accused%20the%20authorities%20of%20kidnapping%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20not%20responded%20to%20AFP%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Madness'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20heavy%20police%20presence%20was%20deployed%20around%20parliament%20early%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20reporter%2C%20the%20smell%20of%20tear%20gas%20still%20in%20the%20air%20and%20dried%20blood%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20policeman%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20broken%20barricades%20to%20the%20complex%20told%20AFP%20he%20had%20watched%20the%20scenes%20unfold%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20madness%2C%20we%20hope%20it%20will%20be%20calm%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20central%20business%20district%2C%20where%20the%20protests%20have%20been%20concentrated%2C%20traders%20surveyed%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20leave%20anything%2C%20just%20the%20boxes.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20long%20it%20will%20take%20me%20to%20recover%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Ng'ang'a%2C%20whose%20electronics%20shop%20was%20looted%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unrest%20has%20alarmed%20the%20international%20community%2C%20with%20Washington%20calling%20on%20Kenya%20to%20respect%20the%20right%20to%20peaceful%20protest%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuto's%20administration%20is%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20IMF%2C%20which%20has%20urged%20the%20country%20to%20implement%20fiscal%20reforms%20in%20order%20to%20access%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719424440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fc99p1s18_kenya-violence-afp_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkenyas-u-turn-over-tax-hikes-after-22-die-in-violent-protests-5977052%22%2C%22summary%22%3