20Ranjit%20Singh's%20statue%20at%20Gurdwara%20Darbar%20Sahib%2C%20Kartarpur%20Sahib%2C%20today%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20local%20and%20Indian%20Sikhs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Arora%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20restored%20statue%20is%20placed%20at%20Kartarpur%20Sahib%20primarily%20so%20that%20Indian%20Sikhs%20visiting%20here%20across%20the%20border%20using%20the%20corridor%20could%20also%20see%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Kartarpur%2C%20better%20security%20will%20also%20be%20ensured%20for%20the%20statue%20of%20the%20Sikh%20leader%20that%20was%20vandalised%20earlier%20at%20Lahore%20Fort%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20455%20Sikhs%20who%20arrived%20here%20from%20India%20last%20week%20to%20take%20part%20in%20events%20in%20connection%20with%20Maharaja%20Ranjit%20Singh's%20death%20anniversary%20attended%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20statue.%20They%20will%20stay%20for%20a%20day%20in%20Kartarpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-foot-tall%20bronze%20statue%20of%20Maharaja%20Ranjit%20Singh%20was%20first%20installed%20at%20the%20Lahore%20Fort%20near%20his%20'samadhi'%20in%202019.%20It%20was%20vandalised%20twice%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Tehreek-e-Labbaik%20Pakistan%20(TLP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statue%20of%20the%20great%20Sikh%20ruler%20of%20Punjab%20was%20a%20gift%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20province%20from%20a%20body%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20statue%2C%20which%20depicts%20the%20Maharaja%20on%20horseback%20took%20eight%20months%20to%20complete%20and%20was%20sponsored%20by%20a%20United%20Kingdom-based%20historian%20and%20Sikh%20Khalsa%20(SK)%20Foundation%20head%2C%20Bobby%20Singh%20Bansal.%20The%20weight%20of%20the%20statue%20is%20said%20to%20be%20between%20250%20and%20330%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharaja%20Ranjit%20Singh%20was%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Empire%2C%20which%20ruled%20the%20northwest%20Indian%20subcontinent%20in%20the%20early%20half%20of%20the%2019th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719423000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F1m8od168_maharaja-ranjit-singh-statue-kartarpur-sahib_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharaja-ranjit-singhs-restored-statue-unveiled-at-paks-kartarpur-sahib-5976927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20restored%20statue%20of%20the%20first%20ruler%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Empire%2C%20Maharaja%20Ranjit%20Singh%2C%20which%20was%20earlier%20damaged%20by%20religious%20extremists%2C%20was%20unveiled%20at%20Kartarpur%20Sahib%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20over%20450%20visiting%20Indian%20Sikhs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharaja-ranjit-singhs-restored-statue-unveiled-at-paks-kartarpur-sahib-5976927%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharaja-ranjit-singhs-restored-statue-unveiled-at-paks-kartarpur-sahib-5976927%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharaja-ranjit-singhs-restored-statue-unveiled-at-paks-kartarpur-sahib-5976927%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eknath%20Shinde%20Takes%20A%20Swipe%20At%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Over%20'Farewell'%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Wednesday%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20for%20his%20statement%20that%20the%20monsoon%20session%20beginning%20June%2027%20will%20be%20the%20farewell%20session%20of%20the%20MahaYuti%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShouldn't%20he%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20be%20in%20the%20House%20to%20give%20a%20farewell%3F%20Or%20will%20he%20say%20goodbye%20from%20a%20Facebook%20Live%3F%20The%20people%20will%20decide%20whether%20to%20bid%20a%20farewell%2C%26quot%3B%20Shinde%20said%2C%20asserting%20that%20those%20sitting%20in%20the%20government%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20people%20and%20have%20done%20a%20slew%20of%20works%20for%20their%20betterment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20obvious%20reference%20was%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20regular%20use%20of%20Facebook%20Live%20during%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government's%20tenure%2C%20instead%20of%20coming%20to%20the%20Mantralaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%2C%20who%20chaired%20the%20state%20Cabinet%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20also%20criticised%20the%20opposition%20for%20its%20move%20to%20boycott%20the%20customary%20tea%20meeting%20convened%20by%20him%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20last%20session%20of%20the%20present%20state%20Assembly.%20So%20we%20thought%20that%20the%20opposition%20would%20come%20and%20discuss%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20during%20the%20tea%20meeting.%20However%2C%20they%20gave%20a%20letter%20mentioning%20the%20same%20issues%2C%20which%20the%20government%20will%20reply%20to%20in%20the%20House.%20The%20opposition%20is%20confused%2C%26quot%3B%20claimed%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opposition%20may%20have%20got%20momentary%20happiness%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20but%20despite%20all%20the%20attacks%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20as%20he%20reiterated%20that%20the%20opposition%20spread%20a%20fake%20narrative%20that%20changes%20will%20be%20made%20in%20the%20Constitution%20and%20reservation%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98'Despite%20spreading%20such%20fake%20narratives%2C%20Congress%20got%20only%2099%20seats%20and%20the%20party%20will%20need%20another%2025%20years%20to%20win%20240%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20camp%20were%20pitted%20against%20each%20other%20in%2013%20seats%2C%20of%20which%20we%20won%20seven%20seats.%20Of%20the%20total%2019%20per%20cent%20votes%2C%20bow%20%26amp%3B%20arrow%20(Sena%20symbol)%20got%2014.50%20per%20cent.%20So%20what%20did%20the%20Thackeray%20cam%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20Shinde%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719422940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fe8or15qg_eknath-shinde-58-vardhapan-din_625x300_19_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-takes-a-swipe-at-uddhav-thackeray-over-farewell-remark-5976921%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Wednesday%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20for%20his%20statement%20that%20the%20monsoon%20session%20beginning%20June%2027%20will%20be%20the%20farewell%20session%20of%20the%20MahaYuti%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-takes-a-swipe-at-uddhav-thackeray-over-farewell-remark-5976921%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-takes-a-swipe-at-uddhav-thackeray-over-farewell-remark-5976921%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-takes-a-swipe-at-uddhav-thackeray-over-farewell-remark-5976921%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20pardons%20US%20veterans%20convicted%20in%20gay-sex%20cases%20by%20military%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719422527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3