l%20Nadu%20government%20to%20submit%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20report%26quot%3B%20after%20a%20Reuters%20story%20revealed%20that%20Apple%20supplier%20Foxconn%20rejected%20married%20women%20from%20iPhone%20assembly%20jobs%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20calling%20for%20the%20probe%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20cited%20the%20Equal%20Remuneration%20Act%20of%201976%2C%20saying%20the%20law%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20stipulates%20that%20no%20discrimination%20(is)%20to%20be%20made%20while%20recruiting%20men%20and%20women%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20it%20has%20requested%20a%20detailed%20report%20from%20the%20Labour%20Department%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20site%20of%20a%20major%20iPhone%20factory%20where%20Reuters%20uncovered%20Foxconn's%20practice%20of%20shunning%20married%20women%20from%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Labour%20Ministry%20said%20it%20also%20directed%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Regional%20Chief%20Labour%20Commissioner%20to%20provide%20a%20%26quot%3Bfactual%20report.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20and%20Foxconn%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20government%20statement.%20The%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20government%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Reuters'%20request%20for%20comment%20outside%20office%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Reuters%20investigation%20published%20on%20Tuesday%20found%20that%20Foxconn%20has%20systematically%20excluded%20married%20women%20from%20jobs%20at%20its%20main%20India%20iPhone%20plant%20near%20Chennai%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20on%20the%20grounds%20they%20have%20more%20family%20responsibilities%20than%20their%20unmarried%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFoxconn%20hiring%20agents%20and%20HR%20sources%20interviewed%20by%20Reuters%20cited%20family%20duties%2C%20pregnancy%20and%20higher%20absenteeism%20as%20reasons%20why%20Foxconn%20did%20not%20hire%20married%20women%20at%20the%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20%26quot%3Btakes%20note%20of%20media%20reports%20on%20married%20women%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20work%20at%20Foxconn%20India%20Apple%20iPhone%20plant%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20response%20to%20questions%20from%20Reuters%20for%20its%20Tuesday%20report%2C%20Apple%20and%20Foxconn%20acknowledged%20lapses%20in%20hiring%20practices%20in%202022%20and%20said%20they%20had%20worked%20to%20address%20the%20issues.%20All%20the%20discriminatory%20practices%20documented%20by%20Reuters%20at%20the%20Sriperumbudur%20plant%2C%20however%2C%20took%20place%20in%202023%20and%202024.%20The%20two%20companies%20didn't%20address%20the%202023%20and%202024%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20concerns%20about%20hiring%20practices%20were%20first%20raised%20in%202022%20we%20immediately%20took%20action%20and%20worked%20with%20our%20supplier%20to%20conduct%20monthly%20audits%20to%20identify%20issues%20and%20ensure%20that%20our%20high%20standards%20are%20upheld%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20all%20its%20suppliers%2C%20including%20Foxconn%2C%20hire%20married%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFoxconn%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bvigorously%20refutes%20allegations%20of%20employment%20discrimination%20based%20on%20marital%20status%2C%20gender%2C%20religion%20or%20any%20other%20form.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20told%20Reuters%20Indian%20law%20doesn't%20bar%20companies%20from%20discriminating%20in%20hiring%20based%20on%20marital%20status.%20Apple's%20and%20Foxconn's%20policies%2C%20however%2C%20prohibit%20such%20hiring%20practices%20in%20their%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719422220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F0juf8c8_foxconn-ch