mp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20Comeback%2C%20What%20PM%20Modi%20Had%20Told%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Sam%20Pitroda%20--%20who%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post%20of%20its%20overseas%20unit%20chief%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20general%20election%20--%20is%20back%20in%20the%20saddle%20again.%20That%20he%20would%20be%20reinstated%2C%20was%20said%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20sometimes%20think%20the%20party%20(the%20Congress)%2C%20in%20a%20well-planned%20way%2C%20does%20this.%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20(the%20members)%20do%20this%20on%20their%20own.%20Then%20they%20are%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20party%20for%20a%C2%A0%20few%20days.%20Then%20they%20come%20back%20in%20the%20mainstream%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20they%20did%20with%20their%20guru%20in%20America.%20He%20has%20resigned.%20Now%20he%20will%20be%20brought%20back%20again%20after%20a%20while...%20It%20is%20their%20well-considered%20strategy%20to%20create%20confusion%20in%20the%20country%2C%20change%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20create%20new%20issues%2C%20compel%20their%20opponents%20to%20react%20on%20these%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Pitroda%20had%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post%20after%20his%20two%20consecutive%20statements%20sparked%20huge%20controversies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20The%20Statesman%20in%20early%20May%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20described%20India%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B...%20diverse%20country...%20where%20people%20on%20East%20look%20like%20the%20Chinese%2C%20people%20on%20West%20look%20like%20Arabs%2C%20people%20in%20the%20North%20look%20like%20maybe%20White%20and%20people%20in%20South%20look%20like%20Africans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20triggered%20allegations%20of%20racism%20and%20