ps%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmad-mad-world%2Fgassy-cows-and-pigs-will-face-a-carbon-tax-in-denmark-a-world-first%2Famp_articleshow%2F111293807.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmad-mad-world%2Fgassy-cows-and-pigs-will-face-a-carbon-tax-in-denmark-a-world-first%2Famp_articleshow%2F111293807.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20%26quot%3BAssurance%26quot%3B%2C%20Sam%20Pitroda%20Reappointed%20Overseas%20Congress%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHaving%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post%20after%20two%20of%20his%20remarks%20stirred%20up%20a%20huge%20political%20row%2C%20putting%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20during%20the%20all-important%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Sam%20Pitroda%20has%20been%20reappointed%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reappointment%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20party%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%20and%2C%20later%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20Mr%20Pitroda%20clarified%20the%20context%20of%20the%20statements%20and%20gave%20an%20assurance%20that%20he%20will%20not%20%26quot%3Bleave%20room%20for%20such%20controversies%20to%20arise%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20recent%20election%20campaign%20Sam%20Pitroda%20had%20made%20some%20statements%20and%20comments%20that%20were%20totally%20unacceptable%20to%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20By%20mutual%20consent%20he%20stepped%20down%20as%20Chairman%20of%20Overseas%20Indian%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20recent%20election%20campaign%20Sam%20Pitroda%20had%20made%20some%20statements%20and%20comments%20that%20were%20totally%20unacceptable%20to%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20By%20mutual%20consent%20he%20stepped%20down%20as%20Chairman%20of%20Overseas%20Indian%20Congress.%20Subsequently%20he%20clarified%20the%20context%20in%20which%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1805997762645024790%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubsequently%20he%20clarified%20the%20context%20in%20which%20statements%20were%20made%20and%20how%20they%20were%20later%20distorted%20by%20the%20Modi%20campaign.%20The%20Congress%20President%20has%20reappointed%20him%20on%20the%20assurance%20that%20he%20will%20not%20in%20future%20leave%20room%20for%20such%20controversies%20to%20arise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C%20when%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20elections%20was%20over%20and%20the%20Congress%20was%20fending%20off%20a%20charge%20-%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20that%20its%20manifesto%20had%20spoken%20of%20wealth%20redistribution%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20had%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20by%20speaking%20about%20an%20inheritance%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20claiming%20that%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20spoke%20of%20snatching%20gold%20and%20women's%20mangalsutras%20(a%20sacred%20ornament%20in%20Hinduism%20symbolising%20that%20a%20woman%20is%20married)%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20ended%20up%20talking%20about%20the%20inheritance%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20America%2C%20there%20is%20an%20inheritance%20tax.%20If%20one%20has%20%24100%20million%20worth%20of%20wealth%20and%20when%20he%20dies%20he%20can%20only%20transfer%20probably%2045%20per%20cent%20to%20his%20children%2C%2055%20per%20cent%20is%20grabbed%20by%20the%20government.%20That's%20an%20interesting%20law.%20It%20says%20you%20in%20your%20generation%2C%20made%20wealth%20and%20you%20are%20leaving%20now%2C%20you%20must%20leave%20your%20wealth%20for%20the%20public%2C%20not%20all%20of%20it%2C%20half%20of%20it%2C%20which%20to%20me%20sounds%20fair%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20latched%20on%20to%20this%20statement%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress'%20hidden%20designs%20had%20been%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20advisor%20of%20the%20prince%20of%20the%20Congress%20royal%20family%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20middle%20class%20should%20be%20taxed%20more.%20Now%20they%20have%20gone%20further%20ahead.%20Now%20the%20Congress%20is%20saying%20that%20it%20will%20impose%20an%20Inheritance%20Tax%20and%20tax%20the%20inheritance%20received%20by%20people%20from%20their%20parents.%20The%20wealth%20you%20accumulate%20with%20your%20hard%20work%20won't%20pass%20down%20to%20your%20children.%20The%20Congress's%20hand%20will%20snatch%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Congress%20was%20dealing%20with%20the%20fallout%20of%20that%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20ended%20up%20making%20another%20controversial%20comment%20in%20early%20May%2C%20which%20led%20to%20allegations%20of%20the%20party%20being%20divisive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20The%20Statesman%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20described%20India%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B...%20diverse%20country...%20where%20people%20on%20East%20look%20like%20Chinese%2C%20people%20on%20West%20look%20like%20Arab%2C%20people%20in%20the%20North%20look%20like%20maybe%20White%20and%20people%20in%20South%20look%20like%20Africa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20controversy%20over%20this%20remark%20snowballed%2C%20the%20Congress%20announced%20on%20May%208%20that%20Mr%20Pitroda%20had%20decided%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn