%3Bvery%20very%20serious%26quot%3B%20issue%20must%20be%20dealt%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20D%20K%20Upadhyaya%20and%20Justice%20Amit%20Borkar%20said%20it%20will%20hold%20the%20top%20officials%20of%20both%20the%20Central%20and%20Western%20Railways%20accountable%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsituation%20in%20Mumbai%20is%20pathetic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PIL%20was%20filed%20by%20Yatin%20Jadhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20very%20serious%20issue%20has%20been%20raised%20in%20the%20PIL%20and%20therefore%20you%20(railway%20authorities)%20have%20to%20address%20it.%20You%20can't%20say%2C%20we%20can't%20do%20this%20or%20can't%20do%20that%20due%20to%20the%20large%20number%20of%20people%20(in%20the%20city).%20You%20carry%20people%20like%20cattle.%20We%20feel%20ashamed%20at%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20commuters%20are%20made%20to%20commute%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20directed%20the%20general%20managers%20(GM)%20of%20the%20Western%20and%20Central%20Railways%20to%20%26quot%3Blook%20into%20the%20entire%20issue%26quot%3B%20and%20file%20affidavits%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavits%20shall%20be%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20vetted%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20GMs%20and%20%26quot%3Bindicate%20the%20measures%20which%20are%20available%20and%20are%20in%20force%20to%20check%20such%20mishaps%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20hear%20the%20PIL%20next%20after%20eight%20weeks%2C%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20petition%2C%202%2C590%20commuters%20lost%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20tracks%20in%202023%2C%20which%20was%20seven%20deaths%20every%20day.%20As%20many%20as%202%2C441%20persons%20were%20injured%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%201%2C650%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20accidents%20on%20the%20Central%20Railway%20route%2C%20940%20died%20on%20the%20Western%20Railway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Suresh%20Kumar%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Western%20Railway%2C%20said%20it%20was%20taking%20measures%20such%20as%20putting%20up%20barricades%20between%20tracks%20and%20construction%20of%20two%20or%20three%20foot-over-bridges%20at%20every%20station.%20The%20WR%20has%20implemented%20HC%20directions%20passed%20in%20an%20earlier%20PIL%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20not%20depend%20only%20on%20orders%20for%20saving%20people's%20lives.%20We%20agree%20you%20have%20followed%20those%20directions.%20But%20have%20you%20been%20able%20to%20check%20these%20deaths%3F%20Question%20is%20whether%20it%20(measures)%20has%20yielded%20results%3F%20Have%20you%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20or%20stop%20deaths%2C%26quot%3B%20asked%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20WR%20was%20running%20services%20at%20the%20highest%20possible%20frequency%2C%20with%20trains%20leaving%20every%202-3%20minutes%20during%20peak%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20it%20was%20not%20suggesting%20that%20the%20Railways%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20trains%20or%20their%20capacity%2C%20but%20a%20solution%20has%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20time%20we%20will%20make%20the%20highest-level%20officers%20accountable.%20The%20situation%20in%20Mumbai%20is%20pathetic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20(Railways)%20can't%20feel%20happy%20that%20you%20have%20been%20ferrying%2035%20lakh%20people%20daily.%20You%20can't%20say%20considering%20the%20number%20of%20people%20in%20Mumbai%20you%20are%20doing%20a%20good%20job.%20You%20can't%20even%20take%20a%20refuge%20saying%20there%20are%20too%20many%20people.%20You%20have%20to%20change%20your%20mindset.%20Your%20officers%20need%20not%20be%20satisfied%20by%20commuting%20such%20a%20large%20number%20of%20commuters%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20a