would%20face%20this%20headlong.%20I%20decided%20to%20double%20my%20willpower%20to%20survive%20and%20that%20has%20been%20my%20best%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20Ask%20him%20how%20he%20feels%20about%20having%20recovered%2C%20and%20he%20says%20%E2%80%9Cone%20day%20at%20a%20time%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CRecovered%20is%20not%20the%20right%20word.%20My%20injections%20and%20medicines%20are%20still%20ongoing.%20And%20so%2C%20I%20keep%20telling%20myself%20that%20in%20whatever%20time%20I%20have%2C%20I%20want%20to%20do%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20reaching%20out%20to%20kids%20visited%20Shyam%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eduring%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20the%20cancer%20ward.%20While%20contemplating%20his%20own%20fate%2C%20he%20would%20watch%20children%20as%20young%20as%20a%20few%20months%20old%20being%20admitted%20for%20cancer%20treatment.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20so%20sad%20to%20watch%20these%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20observations%20set%20a%20precedent%20for%20the%20way%20he%20wanted%20to%20live%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F0i0mTQjhd54%3Fsi%3D62ghizz2KnFUS5Lm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20soon%20realised%20that%20coaxing%20kids%2C%20who%20did%20not%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338306%2Fias-officer-shubham-gupta-used-artificial-intelligence-to-fight-malnutrition-govt-schools-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20basic%20hygiene%2C%20to%20study%2C%20was%20counterproductive.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20need%20a%20good%20environment%20to%20study%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reiterates.%20And%20so%2C%20Shyam%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20centres%