C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAssam%E2%80%99s%20maternal%20mortality%20ratio%20was%20also%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%20back%20then%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20so%20even%20today%20despite%20the%20slight%20improvement%20%5B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F44379%2Fdownload%2F48052%2FSRS_MMR_Bulletin_2018_2020.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E195%20per%20100%2C000%20live%20births%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Assam%2C%20there%20are%202%2C500%20islands%20and%20most%20of%20them%20are%20inhabited.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20an%20idea%20that%20involved%20the%20support%20of%20local%20people%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20people%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20conditions%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%20especially%20the%20women%20and%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20build%20roads%20everywhere%20and%20certainly%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20helicopters%20give%20services%20throughout%20the%20year.%20So%2C%20we%20shifted%20to%20the%20traditional%20system%20of%20using%20boats%20and%20to%20look%20upon%20the%20river%20as%20an%20ally%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%2C%20the%20non-profit%20launched%20the%20boat%20clinics%20in%202005%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide.%20Since%20then%2C%20monthly%20health%20camps%20have%20been%20organised%20across%2014%20districts%20including%20Dibrugarh%2C%20Tinsukia%2C%20Jorhat%2FMajuli%2C%20Sonitpur%2C%20and%20Nalbari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%2015%20such%20floating%20health%20clinics%20are%20operating%20along%20the%20river%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20isolated%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20a%20team%20comprising%20two%20medical%20officers%2C%20laboratory%20technician%2C%20pharmacist%2C%20and%20three%20nurses%20reach%20out%20to%20offer%20primary%20healthcare%20at%20the%20island%20itself.%20These%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20vaccines%20for%20newborn%20babies%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20measles%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20polio%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20conducts%20routine%20immunisations%20for%20pregnant%20women%20and%20also%20has%20a%20provision%20to%20test%20haemoglobin%2C%20blood%20glucose%20levels%2C%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%2C%20and%20tuberculosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team's%20focus%20is%20on%20routine%20immunisation%2C%20primary%20healthcare%20services%2C%20child%20and%20antenatal%20care.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354367%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%E2%80%99s%20focus%20is%20on%20routine%20immunisation%2C%20primary%20healthcare%20services%2C%20child%20and%20antenatal%20care.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolar%20energy%20to%20the%20rescue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20in%20running%20the%20programme%2C%20Riturekha%20Barua%2C%20the%20district%20programme%20officer%20of%20Majuli%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20we%20have%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20boats%20for%2018%20days%20in%20a%20month.%20The%20boat%20was%20our%20home.%20So%2C%20while%20patients%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20we%20could%20not.%20We%20slept%20in%20our%20respective%20beddings%20here%2C%20far%20away%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20our%20homes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20kerosene-based%20generators%20for%20power%20but%20it%20would%20only%20help%20for%203%20to%204%20hours%20in%20a%20day.%20It%20would%20become%20challenging%20and%20uneasy%20for%20us%20to%20live%20on%20the%20boat%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20summer%20heat.%20Secondly%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20cold%20storage%20facility%20for%20vaccines.%20Having%20a%20permanent%20energy%20supply%20was%20crucial%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20non-profit%20decided%20to%20harness%20solar%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20C-NES%20partnered%20with%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F114009%2Fboat-clinics-brahmaputra-healthcare-boat-clinics-switching-solar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESELCO%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20works%20to%20bring%20sustainable%20energy%20solutions%20to%20rural%20and%20urban%20communities%20in%20the%20country.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20large%20boats%20were%20equipped%20with%20solar%20panels%20of%203%20KV%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20solar%20power%20can%E2%80%99t%20drive%20vessels%20on%20a%20river%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20So%2C%20we%20use%20it%20to%20run%20lighting%20and%20basic%20services%20like%20fans.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20cold%20chains%20for%20chilling%20units%20which%20store%20and%20carry%20vaccines%20and%20other%20life-saving%20equipment%20are%20also%20solar-powered%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20rows%20from%20village%20to%20village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354369%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20rows%20from%20village%20to%20village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiturekha%20says%20that%20with%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20crew%20has%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply%20for%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saddam%2C%20who%20remains%20in%20the%20boat%20for%20at%20least%20nine%20days%20on%20a%20stretch%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20solar-powered%20chilling%20units%20are%20very%20beneficial%20as%20without%20them%2C%20we%20could%20not%20keep%20the%20vaccines%20for%20more%20than%20three%20days.%20Besides%2C%20it%20is%20really%20helpful%20in%20running%20fans%20all%20day%20as%20it%20is%20extremely%20hot%20and%20humid%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20feel%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20solar%20panels%20should%20be%20increased%20for%20better%20results.%20Last%20night%2C%20the%20solar-powered%20fans%20could%20only%20last%20till%209%3A30.%20We%20had%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20generator%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20night.%20If%20the%20capacity%20is%20increased%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20retire%20to%20bed%20and%20sleep%20peacefully%20after%20a%20hectic%20day%20providing%20quality%20service%20to%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20healthcare%20provider%20believes%20the%20capacity%20must%20be%20increased%2C%20Riturekha%20says%20that%20with%20the%20additional%20support%20of%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20floating%20health%20clinic%20is%20successfully%20catering%20to%20about%2010%2C000%20patients%20in%20the%20district%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20soil%20erosion%20and%20regular%20flooding%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%20to%20build%20a%20permanent%20structure%20in%20these%20places%20which%20leads%20to%20medical%20apathy%20for%20the%20residents.%20But%20with%20these%20boat%20clinics%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20the%20islands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Riturekha%20Barua%20and%20Dr%20Saddam%20Hussain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719404622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20reporting%20from%20rural%20parts%20of%20Assam%2C%20Sanjoy%20Hazarika%20noticed%20the%20intense%20need%20for%20a%20sustained%20healthcare%20system%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20collab