0Gan%2C%20Founder%2C%20Rite%20Water%20Solutions%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20chemical%20to%20biological%20treatment%20of%20water%2C%20Rite%20Water%20Solutions%20has%20now%20established%20over%205%2C200%20community%20water%20purification%20plants%20across%20the%20country.%20Abhijeet%20Gan%2C%20the%2041-year-old%20founder%2C%20claims%20that%20the%20company%20is%20purifying%20over%2010%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20safe%20water%20to%20rural%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20clean%20drinking%20water%2C%20which%20most%20of%20us%20take%20for%20granted%2C%20is%20a%20luxury%20for%20many%20in%20rural%20India.%20The%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20launched%20in%202019%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%20safe%20and%20adequate%20drinking%20water%20through%20individual%20household%20tap%20connections%20to%20all%20rural%20households.%20So%20far%2C%20about%2075%20percent%20of%20rural%20households%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20tap%20water%20connections%2C%20former%20Jal%20Shakti%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20said%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijeet%20Gan%2C%20the%20MD%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20Rite%20Water%20Solutions%2C%20started%20working%20on%20this%20mammoth%20problem%20almost%2018%20years%20ago%2C%20much%20before%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351304%2Fchennai-bengaluru-water-crisis-prashant-sharma-grey-water-recycling-in-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJal%20Jeevan%20mission.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frite3-1718797984.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Rite%20Water%2