ential%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFoundation%20for%20Social%20Town%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-profit%20organisation%20was%20started%20with%20500%20people%20and%20has%20engaged%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20in%20social%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20initially%20used%20WhatsApp%20groups%20and%20emails%20for%20interactions.%20We%20used%20the%20platforms%20to%20dissipate%20important%20information%20about%20policy%20changes%2C%20incubation%20programmes%2C%20and%20more%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20organisation%20does%20not%20charge%20any%20fee%20for%20membership%20and%20is%20open%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20bring%20social%20change.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20more%20like%20a%20community%20of%20people%20with%20a%20similar%20school%20of%20thought%20who%20want%20to%20bring%20some%20kind%20of%20change%20in%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20organisation%20works%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20changemaker%20in%20Kerala%20who%20wants%20to%20help%20a%20dying%20school%20and%20wants%20to%20give%20them%20computer%20systems%20but%20is%20unsure%20of%20which%20companies%20to%20approach%20and%20how%20to%20raise%20the%20funds%2C%20then%20that%20is%20where%20Social%20Town%20steps%20in.%20We%20try%20to%20connect%20them%20with%20the%20right%20people%20and%20help%20them%20raise%20resources.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkber%20Ali%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20who%20works%20with%20the%20tribals%20of%20Wayanad%2C%20points%20out%20the%20importance%20of%20initiatives%20like%20Social%20Town.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20worked%20with%20the%20organisation%20many%20times%20now.%20First%20when%20there%20was%20a%20flood%20back%20in%202019%2C%20then%20during%20a%20landslide%20and%20then%20again%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20When%20you%20work%20in%20remote%20tribal%20areas%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people%20in%20cities%20and%20get%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CNeenu%2C%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20was%20the%20first%20person%20I%20contacted%20to%20help%20us.%20In%20the%20hills%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20basic%20hand%20sanitisers%2C%20she%20was%20the%20one%20who%20raised%20the%20money%2C%20collected%20the%20required%20amenities%2C%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20us.%20Once%2C%20it%20was%20known%20to%20other%20people%20that%20we%20needed%20help%2C%20many%20came%20to%20our%20rescue%20but%20it%20was%20the%20initial%20first%20step%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20people%20that%20the%20organisation%20helped%20us%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22If%20you%20want%20to%20start%20your%20social%20work%20journey%2C%20Social%20Town%20can%20help!%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353678%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20start%20your%20social%20work%20journey%2C%20Social%20Town%20can%2